Package org.usfirst.frc.team4338.robot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BallElevator
    BallElevator.java - robot component of the ball elevator to pick up balls from the floor
    BallShelf
    BallShelf.java - robot component of the ball shelf to more easily pick up ball from a hopper.
    Climber
    Climber.java - robot component of the climbing system to climb the rope.
    Controller
    Controller.java - The controller used to control the robot.
    GearCatcher
    GearCatcher.java - robot component for the gear catching system to catch and release gears.
    Robot
    Robot.java - The main class for the Robot, contains other components of the robot The VM is configured to automatically run this class, and to call the functions corresponding to each mode, as described in the IterativeRobot documentation.
    Shooter
    Shooter.java - robot component of the shooting mechanism.
